				<td colspan="2"><span>Ignorance... oh enemy of mine... 
<br />
Where do those hotkeys go? in the hotkey bar right?
<br />
That prevents me from having my Tiny cloak of darkest nights, weapon/instrument swaping, mez call hotkey, pull hotkey, boastful bellow hotkey, fading memories hotkey. Switching hotkey pages just to twist is very time consuming and quite frankly on a hard LDoN the last thing I wanna do is have to deal with is switching hotkey pages. 
<br />

<br />
Twist less, twist smarter is my motto. 
<br />

<br />
To all you who can twist 4-5-6-7 songs, Grats to you, you do a fine job. Right now I never go LFG and get tells for groups very often, so I must be doing something right =P
<br />

<br />
I can still twist 4 btw, but it's a tight twist (even with hotkeys it seems tight, might be my connection) but I rarely need it. 
