Zoned in, had about 10feet of corridor to a cross roads, and about 5 m obs +1 wanderer there. Had to lull 1, mez pull 3 and then frantically mez the 2 adds and remember to fade. About 2mins after i realised we coulda rooted one, zoned out and come back to the solo one but oh well =) Hindsight is always 20/20 and we still cleared it np and won =)
<br />

<br />
Oh and I generally twist 4 songs: Psalm, muse, Zek, marr.
<br />

<br />
Mezzing I will twist: mez, Zek or muse (depends ifcaster/melee heavy) and Psalm. Only twist 3 mezzing incase of resists.
<br />

<br />
Mezzing 2 or more mobs ill not melee, will stand back, mezz, mezz if both mez lands with 0 resists ill throw in a marr. Mezzing 3+ and ill just mez as fast as ican and scream at someoen to root park tooto help me out =)
<br />

<br />
/shrug everyone plays differently tho, as long as you can be an asset to your group, grats thats all we need to do.  
